{"tid":996003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台主持人力撐用華為 「是我比台獨腦殘優秀的原因」","createTime":"2019-01-26T02:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T11:51:48.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a3e7a1a4d11a78ec900cacbe8b0948404c0926c6","tid":996003,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T02:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190126/large/1548466403_1b04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190126%2Flarge%2F1548466403_1b04.jpg&h=52357b7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣行政院日前指，下周將公佈「行政命令」，禁止台灣公務員使用大陸手機、使用大陸社交媒體；更有指台灣當局正編製一份大陸科技公司的詳細「黑名單」，預計會今年3月底前出爐，華為、聯想等大陸企業也在列。台灣中視新聞台節目主持人黃智賢今日開腔支持中國科技產品，並稱「用華為 是我比台獨腦殘優秀的原因」，文尾還指名道姓，批評台南市急不待及禁用華為一切產品，指其民進黨親生哥哥、即台南市長黃偉哲這樣做很蠢。<br />\n<br />\n黃智賢周六（26日）早上在微博發文，題為〈我當然用華為手機〉，她寫道「我有兩支（部）手機，一支Oppo，一支華為。我佩戴小米手環。這就是我比台獨腦殘優秀的原因」。<br />\n黃智賢還表示，「中國沒有錯，只錯在搶了美國的市場，威脅美國帝國主義霸權。華為更只是因為太優秀，所以被祭旗」。她又表示，微軟、Google、facebook、Line、甚至寶可夢（Pok&eacute;mon Go），都在搜集利用用家資訊，質問「所以台灣人的資料，傳給美國和韓國（南韓），是我們的榮幸？」<br />\n<br />\n她最後指，蔡英文政府不准政府機關用微信、上大陸網站，3月份會公佈完整的禁用名單；而台南市急不待及禁用華為一切產品，在文尾批評其親生哥哥「台南市長黃偉哲，你知道，你這樣做很蠢嗎？」"},{"pid":"813ef52fe1939329957557c71953379b9c0f41ae","tid":996003,"uid":147376,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T02:21:14.000Z","msg":"中視<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n蔡衍明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ebae591baf45d9ded07ecdbc5db430843fbcd5","tid":996003,"uid":170375,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T02:22:44.000Z","msg":"奶阿奶阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153d945fa55805216c31fdc6ff06a9001560139e","tid":996003,"uid":40628,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T02:24:16.000Z","msg":"//歐美學術界已不信任華為，美國各大學也出現「華為寒蟬效應」，開始撤除華為、中興通訊等中國製造的電訊設備，包括加大柏克萊大學（UC Berkeley）、爾灣加大（UC Irvine）、洛杉磯加大（UCLA）、戴維斯加大（UC Davis）及加大聖地牙哥分校（UCSD）。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190126/20599669\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190126%2F20599669&d=UwQMSjbS41QxOfoXNLYtBTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=2b95536d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190126%2F20599669&h=2a3b07c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190126/20599669</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔通佢認為佢比歐美頂尖學府優秀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef821d215992da319d143987f1918744f7e83e3","tid":996003,"uid":208159,"like":2,"dislike":28,"score":-26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T02:46:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f51bc1f88b01add9a0efa45194f80136b495edf8","tid":996003,"uid":150609,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T02:57:39.000Z","msg":"其實就係唔想比支那監控<br />\n<br />\n咩facebook google 果d全部都監控架啦 係唔想比你支那監控姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a593ed04b8d66c2e4ca550ccbeee7a19f9297958","tid":996003,"uid":35014,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T03:00:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee15e45b5f509792f58ef5fa24f34e0667602fc3","tid":996003,"uid":39855,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T03:08:49.000Z","msg":"台灣版屈小姐"},{"pid":"a5eda6e0e9ed219c54f98f67deab51c3c2636fa1","tid":996003,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T03:16:47.000Z","msg":"返大陸有錢途"},{"pid":"cf80e37a1788e8c453dab36be9bb38c